      "date": "2012-10-25 12:38:54.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/a6ec53b2-1e9b-11e2-8b41-52540035b04c).  Ran 2 tests.  No failures.",
